title: Te Robaré (Prince Royce song)
text:
"Te Robaré" (<a href="English%20language">English</a>: "I’ll Kidnap You") is a 2013 <a href="Bachata%20%28music%29">bachata</a> song by American recording artist <a href="Prince%20Royce">Prince Royce</a>. The song was released in February 2014 as the second single lifted from Royce's third <a href="studio%20album">studio album</a>, "<a href="Soy%20el%20Mismo%20%28Prince%20Royce%20album%29">Soy el Mismo</a>" (2013).
Music video.
The music video was released on 3 February 2014..
